 Welcome to the LUG Dev Day workshop host.

 ~/lustre-release      Lustre master, pre-cloned.  Your copy --
                       edit, build, push.
 ~/CLAUDE.md           Environment cheat sheet (also AGENTS.md).
                       Read it, or point your agent at it.

 ltvm                  Build + run Lustre microVMs (single global
                       config, shared artifact cache).  Start with:
                         ltvm --help
                         ltvm create <yourname>-testvm1

 Crash analysis        drgn + lustre-drgn-tools installed.  See the
                       "drgn crash analysis" section of CLAUDE.md.

 /shared/<user>/       World-writable drop zone for trading files
                       with other attendees.

 Have fun.  Everything is disposable.
